<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 15:07:48 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1da041aedb9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天，上方，下方。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Blue sky, grey and white clouds ina oberally bright afternoon. " height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a1da041aedb9.jpg" width="1128"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 15:07:48 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>粗糙美味烘焙</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1d9b948dc1a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;它看起来挺粗糙的，但每个人似乎都很喜欢。我承认它看起来很好吃。我一直很喜欢从头开始烘焙。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Three layer chocolate cake with chocolate frosting. About half of it has been eaten, all of it is sliced. One portion is laying on edge." height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/swrogers/6a1d9b948dc1a.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://swrogers.some.pics"&gt;@swrogers&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 14:47:52 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1d469b1c974</link><description>&lt;p&gt;海滩救护队的氛围&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A lone person rides a jet ski across gentle waves at sunset. The low sun glows orange above the horizon, casting warm reflections across the water, while the rider appears as a dark silhouette against the vivid sky." height="2581" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/raeubervater/6a1d469b1c974.jpg" width="3872"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://raeubervater.some.pics"&gt;@raeubervater&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 08:45:18 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a1d0b6dce76e</